

=Bio=

Participates in the Economics Working group and generally in Occupy London since Nov 2011. Member of the School of Commoning. Convenor of the Governance Working Group at Friern Barnet Peoples Library. Also works with "Becoming Catalysts for a Radical Social Movement" Elsewhere he works as a musician and artist.

